{"title":"党支部书记的品格","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":2,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"党支部书记的品格"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要有理想，给人以坚定感；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"善于创新，给人以敏锐感；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"循循善诱，给人以信任感；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关心同志，给人以亲切感；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豁达大度，给人以宽厚感；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一身正气，给人以公正感；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处事冷静，给人以稳重感；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐观风趣，给人以幽默感；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"善于学习，给人以广博感；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以身作则，给人以楷模感。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（２月７日《广州日报》）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}